message.text:
✨🎂 𝐇𝐚𝐩𝐩𝐲 𝐁𝐢𝐫𝐭𝐡𝐝𝐚𝐲, 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐩𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐨𝐧 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐚 𝐏𝐚𝐳 𝐀𝐥𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐭𝐨! 🎂✨

On behalf of your PATA family, we wish you boundless joy, good health, and continued success in the years ahead.

message.text:
✨🎂 𝐇𝐚𝐩𝐩𝐲 𝐁𝐢𝐫𝐭𝐡𝐝𝐚𝐲, 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐩𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐨𝐧 𝐌𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐚 𝐏𝐚𝐳 𝐀𝐥𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐭𝐨! 🎂✨

Today, we celebrate not just your special day, but also your remarkable leadership and dedication to advancing Philippine tourism. 

Your vision continues to inspire the PATA Philippines Chapter to drive tourism forward with passion, collaboration, and purpose. 

On behalf of your PATA family, we wish you boundless joy, good health, and continued success in the years ahead.
